						               													<description>'WITCHES' is a hand management game in which little witches struggle to become a cannabis.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Watch what card the other person is going to play, make predictions.&amp;#10;It's a game where you use your little witch card a little strategic and fun.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. All players start with one witch card in each color, two fake cards, and three physical coins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2. Mix the remaining witch cards well and center the 'Great Witch' card and 18 physical coins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;3. There are two more chances each turn for the player to have a witch card before attacking the 'Great Witch'.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;4. Players prepare to attack the 'Great Witch' by combining 3 cards with the same color witch card and fake card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;5. Once all players have finished selecting their cards, they will release them simultaneously to attack the 'Great Witch' according to their decision.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;6. Depending on the remaining physical strength of the 'The Great Witch', the player is attacked by releasing one or two sheets in order from the pile of witch cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;7-1. When the 'Great Witch's physical strength is below zero, the player with the most physical coins wins (if the same physical coin, the person with fewer cards) and becomes the 'Great Witch'.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;7-2. If all but one player loses stamina, the last player becomes the 'god witch' and wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
